{
    "747:0": "kaṭhinavastu",
    "747:1": "(kaṭhinavastuni piṇḍo )ddānam |",
    "747:2": "sāketena hi kasyacid vicāritaṃ marditaṃ cāpyakālena pudgalaḥ |",
    "747:3": "mātṛkāpadānyakṛtena (hi)",
    "747:4": "viṃśatiḥ karaṇīyena (tu)",
    "747:5": "dvādaśikāḥ ||",
    "747:6": "(uddānam)",
    "747:7": "sāketena varṣopagatā śāsturdaṃrśanakāmyayā |",
    "747:8": "kardame uṣṇena klāntānāṃ cīvaraṃ tatra saṃmatam ||1||",
    "747:9": "buddho bhagavān śrāvastyāṃ varṣā upagato jetavane anāthapiṇḍa (da) syārāme |",
    "747:10": "tena khalu samayema saṃbahulā bhikṣavaḥ sākete varṣā upagatāḥ |",
    "747:11": "trayāṇāṃ vārṣikāṇāṃ māsānāmatyayāt kṛtyacīvarā niṣṭhitacīvarāḥ samādāya pātracīvaraṃ bahutṛṇe bahukardame uṣṇena klalāmyantaḥ svedaparyākuryākulīkṛtaśarīrā yena śrāvastīṃ tena cārikāṃ carantaḥ śrāvastīmanuprāptaḥ |",
    "747:12": "atha saṃbahulā bhikṣavaḥ pātracīvaraṃ pratiśamayya pādau prakṣālya yena bhagavāṃstenopasaṃkrāntāḥ |",
    "747:13": "upasaṃkrasya bhagavataḥ pādau śirasā vanditvā ekāntaniṣaṇṇāḥ |",
    "747:14": "dharmatā khalu buddhā bhagavantaḥ āgantukān bhikṣūnanayā pratisaṃmodanayā pratisaṃmodante kuto yūyaṃ bhikṣava etarhyāgacchatha |",
    "747:15": "kutra vāstha |",
    "747:16": "varṣā uṣitā iti |",
    "747:17": "pratisaṃmodate bhagavanāgantukān bhikṣūnanayā pratisaṃmodanayā |",
    "747:18": "sukhasparśaṃ varṣā neyāḥ |",
    "747:19": "kuto yūyaṃ bhikṣava etarhyāgacchatha |",
    "747:20": "kutrā vāstha |",
    "747:21": "varṣā uṣitāḥ |",
    "747:22": "te kathayanti |",
    "747:23": "sāketādvayaṃ bhadanta etarhyāgacchāmaḥ |",
    "747:24": "sākete vāsma |",
    "747:25": "varṣā uṣitāḥ |",
    "747:26": "kaccidyuyaṃ bhikṣavaḥ sākete sukhasparśaṃ varṣā uṣitā na vāstha klāntāḥ piṇḍakena |",
    "747:27": "tathyam |",
    "747:28": "vayaṃ bhadanta sākete sukhasparśaṃ varṣā uṣitāḥ |",
    "747:29": "na vāsma klāntāḥ piṇḍakena |",
    "747:30": "apitu vayaṃ samādāya pātracīvaraṃ bahutṛṇe bahukardame uṣṇena klāmyantaḥ svadeparyākulīkṛtaśarīrā janapadacārikāṃ carantaḥ kṛcchreṇehānuprāptāḥ |",
    "747:31": "bhagavān saṃlakṣayati |",
    "747:32": "klāmyanti vata me śrāvakāḥ |",
    "747:33": "samādāya pātracīvaraṃ bahutṛṇe bahukardame uṣṇena klāmyanti svedaparyākulīkṛtaśarīrā janapadacārikāṃ carantaḥ yattvahaṃ bhikṣuṇāṃ svarśavihārārthaṃ dātṝṇāṃ ca deyadharmaparibhogārthaṃ bhikṣuṇāṃ kaṭhinamanujānīyāṃ yasmātpaṃcānuśaṃsāḥ kaṭhināstare |",
    "747:34": "na daśāhaparamaṃ na māsaparamaṃ na rātripravāsaḥ sāntarottareṇa cīvareṇ ajanapadacārikāprakramaṇaṃ yāvadāptaṃ vikalpakacīvaradhāraṇamiti |",
    "747:35": "apare'pi paṃcānuśaṃsāḥ |",
    "747:36": "na gaṇabhoganaṃ na paraṃparabhojanaṃ na kuleṣvanimantritacārikā yāvadāptaṃ cīvaraparyeṣaṇam |",
    "747:37": "kārtikānmāsād yāvatphālguno māso'trāntarādāstṛtakaṭhi (nā)",
    "747:38": "nāṃ lābha iti viditvā bhikṣūnāmantrayate sma |",
    "747:39": "tasmāttarhi bhikṣavo'nujānāmi bhikṣuṇāṃ sparśavihārārthaṃ dātṝṇāṃ cā deyadharmaparibhogārtham |",
    "747:40": "varṣoṣitairbhikṣurbhiḥ kaṭhinamāstartavyam yasmātpaṃcānuśaṃsāḥ kaṭhine |",
    "747:41": "na daśāhaparamaṃ pūrvavadyāvadāstṛtakaṭhinānāṃ (lābhaḥ) khyāta iti |",
    "747:42": "uktaṃ bhagavatā kaṭhinamāstartavyamiti |",
    "747:43": "bhikṣavo na jānate kathamāstartavyamiti |",
    "747:44": "bhagavānāha |",
    "747:45": "yadvarṣoṣitasya saṃghasya cīvaralābhaḥ saṃpadyate tasmādāstartavyam |",
    "747:46": "evaṃ ca punarāstartavyam |",
    "747:47": "pūrvavt sāmagnyamārocayitavyam |",
    "747:48": "idaṃ cīvaram |",
    "747:49": "varṣoṣitasya saṃghasya cīvaralābhaḥ sampannaḥ |",
    "747:50": "yadi saṃghasyābhirucitamanena cīvareṇa saṃgahsya kaṭhinaāstariṣyati |",
    "747:51": "tataḥ paścāt aparasmim divase śayanāsanaprajñaptiṃ kṛtvā gaṇḍīmākoṭya pṛṣṭavācikayā bhikṣūn samanuyujya sarvasaṃghe saṃniṣaṇṇe saṃnipatite ekena bhikṣuṇā jñaptiṃ kṛtvā karma kartavyam |",
    "747:52": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:53": "idaṃ cīvaram |",
    "747:54": "varṣiṣitasya saṃghasya cīvaralābhaḥ saṃpannaḥ |",
    "747:55": "saṃghasya kaṭhinamabhirucitamanena cīvareṇa kaṭhinamāstaritum |",
    "747:56": "yenāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsātprakrāmataḥ purāṇacīvarāṇāmapyavipravāso bhaviṣyati prāgeva navakānām |",
    "747:57": "sacetsaṃghasya prāptakālaḥ kṣametānujānīyāt saṃghoyatsaṃghaḥ idaṃ cīvaraṃ kaṭhinārthaṃ saṃmantheta |",
    "747:58": "anena cīvareṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:59": "yenāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsātprakrāmataḥ purāṇacīvarāṇāmapyavipravāso bhaviṣyati prāgeva navakānāmityeṣā jñaptiḥ |",
    "747:60": "evaṃ ca karma kartavyam |",
    "747:61": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:62": "idaṃ cīvaram |",
    "747:63": "varṣiṣitam |",
    "747:64": "saṃghasya cīvaralābhaḥ saṃpannaḥ |",
    "747:65": "saṃghasya cābhirucitaṃ kaṭhinaṃ startum |",
    "747:66": "tatsaṃgha idaṃ cīvaraṃ kaṭhinārthaṃ saṃmanyate |",
    "747:67": "anena cīvareṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:68": "yenāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsātprakrāmataḥ purāṇacīvarakāṇāmapyavipravāso bhaviṣyati prāgeva navakānām |",
    "747:69": "yeṣāmāyuṣmatām kṣamate idaṃ cīvaraṃ kaṭhinārthaṃ saṃmantumanena cīvareṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati|",
    "747:70": "yenāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsātprakrāmataḥ purāṇacīvarakāṇāmapyavipravāso bhaviṣyati prāgeva navakānām |",
    "747:71": "sa tūṣṇīm |",
    "747:72": "na kṣḥamate bhāṣatām |",
    "747:73": "saṃmataḥ saṃghena idaṃ cīvaraṃ kaṭhinārtham |",
    "747:74": "anena cīvareṇa kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:75": "yenāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsātprakrāmataḥ purāṇacīvarakāṇāmapyavipravāso bhaviṣyati prāgeva navakānām |",
    "747:76": "kṣāntamanujñātaṃ saṃghena yasmāttūṣṇīmevametaddhārayāmi |",
    "747:77": "tataḥ paścātkaṭhināstārako bhikṣuḥ saṃmantavyaḥ |",
    "747:78": "paṃcabhirdharmaiḥ samanvāgataḥ kaṭhināstārako bhikṣurasaṃmato na saṃmantavyaḥ saṃmataścāvakāśayitavyaḥ |",
    "747:79": "katamaiḥ pañcabhiḥ |",
    "747:80": "avārṣiko varṣācchinnakaḥ paścimakāṃ varṣāmupagato'nyatra varṣoṣitaḥ śikṣādattakaḥ |",
    "747:81": "aparairapi paṃcabhirna saṃmantavyaḥ |",
    "747:82": "pāricāsiko mūlapārivāsiko mānāpya (cāro)",
    "747:83": "mūlamānāpyacāra utkṣiptakaḥ |",
    "747:84": "apare paṃca na saṃmantavyāḥ |",
    "747:85": "chandādṛ gacchati bhayād dveṣānmohād bhayād gacchati |",
    "747:86": "āstṛtaṃ cānāstṛtaṃ kaṭhinaṃ na jānāti |",
    "747:87": "paṃcabhistu dharmaiḥ samanvāgataḥ kaṭhināstārako bhikṣurasaṃmataśca saṃmantavyaḥ saṃmataśca (nā)",
    "747:88": "vakāśayitavyaḥ |",
    "747:89": "katamaiḥ pañcabhiḥ |",
    "747:90": "na cchandād gacchati na dveṣānna mohānna bhayād gacchati |",
    "747:91": "āstṛtānāstṛtaṃ ca kaṭhinaṃ jānāti |",
    "747:92": "evaṃ ca punaḥ saṃmantavyaḥ |",
    "747:93": "śayanāsanaprajñaptiṃ kṛtvā pūrvavadyāvadutsāhayitavyaḥ |",
    "747:94": "utsahase tvamevaṃ nāmā saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstartumiti |",
    "747:95": "sacedutsahate na vaktavyamutsahediti |",
    "747:96": "tataḥ paścādekena bhikṣuṇā jñaptiṃ kṛtvā karma kartavyam |",
    "747:97": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghah |",
    "747:98": "ayamevaṃnāmā kaṭhināstārako bhikṣurutsahate saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:99": "sa cetsaṃghasya prāptakāla kṣematānujānīyāt saṃgho yatsaṃghaḥ evaṃnāmānaṃ kaṭhināstārakam |",
    "747:100": "saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:101": "yeṣāmāyuṣmatām kṣamante evaṃ nāmānaṃ kaṭhināstārakaṃ saṃmantum |",
    "747:102": "evaṃ nāmā kaṭhināstārakaḥ saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:103": "te tūṣṇīm |",
    "747:104": "na kṣamante bhāṣantām |",
    "747:105": "saṃmataḥ saṃghena evaṃnāmā kaṭhināstārakaḥ saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyati |",
    "747:106": "kṣāntamanujñātaṃ saṃghena |",
    "747:107": "yasmāttūṣṇīmevametaddhārayāmi |",
    "747:108": "tataḥ kaṭhināstārakasya bhikṣorjñaptyā kaṭhinamāstaritavyam |",
    "747:109": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:110": "idaṃ cīvaraṃ saṃġhena kaṭhinārthaṃ saṃmatam |",
    "747:111": "ayaṃ caivaṃnāmā kaṭhināstārako bhikṣuḥ saṃmataḥ |",
    "747:112": "sa cetsaṃghasya prāptakālaṃ kṣametānujānīyāt saṃgho yatsaṃghaḥ idaṃ cīvaraṃ kaṭhinārthamevaṃnāmno bhikṣoranupradadyādityeṣāṃ jñaptiḥ |",
    "747:113": "kaṭhināstārakasyāhaṃ bhikṣurāsamudācārikān dharmān prajñapayiṣyāmi |",
    "747:114": "kaṭhināstārakeṇa bhikṣuṇā kaṭhinena sarvaṃ tu pūrvaṃgamena bhavitavyam |",
    "747:115": "dhāvatā vitaratācchindatā sīvatā raṃjayatā |",
    "747:116": "antato dvau trayo vā sūcīpadakā dātavyāḥ |",
    "747:117": "dvau trayo vā cittotpādā utpādayitavyāḥ |",
    "747:118": "tataḥ paścādāśvayujamāse śuklapakṣe paṃcadaśyāmārocayitavyam |",
    "747:119": "śvo'hamāyuṣmantaḥ kaṭhinamāstariṣyāmi |",
    "747:120": "yuṣmābhiḥ svakasvakāni cīvarāṇi prayudvartavyānīti |",
    "747:121": "tataḥ kaṭhināstārakeṇa bhikṣuṇā kaṭhinaṃ gandhapuṣpānvitaṃ surabhudhūpadhūpitaṃ kṛtvā śayanāsanaprajñaptikṛtvā gaṇḍīmākoṭya pṛṣṭavācikayā bhikṣūn samanuyujya sarvasaṃghe saṃniṣaṇṇe saṃnipatite vṛddhānte sthāpayitavyam |",
    "747:122": "tato vṛddhānte sthitvā kaṭhina gṛhītvā vaktavyam |",
    "747:123": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:124": "idaṃ cīvaram saṃghena kaṭhinaṃ saṃmatam |",
    "747:125": "ahaṃ caivaṃnāmā bhikṣuḥ kaṭhināstārakah |",
    "747:126": "so'hamevaṃnāmā kaṭhināstārakastena vīcarakeṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:127": "evaṃ dvirapi trirapi |",
    "747:128": "tata āstīrya saṃghasyavirasya purastāt sthitvā evaṃ vaktavyam |",
    "747:129": "samanvāhara sthavira idaṃ cīvaraṃ saṃghena kaṭhinaṃ asṃmatam |",
    "747:130": "ahaṃ caivaṃnāmā kaṭhināstārakaḥ |",
    "747:131": "tanmayā anena cīvareṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstṛtamiti |",
    "747:132": "tena vaktavyam |",
    "747:133": "sādhvāstṛtaṃ suṣṭhvā stṛtam |",
    "747:134": "yotra lābhaścānuśaṃsaśca so'smākamiti |",
    "747:135": "evaṃ dvirapi trirapi yāvatsaṃghanavakasya sarvairvaktavyam |",
    "747:136": "sādhvāstṛtaṃ suṣṭhvāstṛtam |",
    "747:137": "yo'tra lābhaścānuśaṃsaśca so'smākamiti |",
    "747:138": "kaṭhināstārakeṇa bhikṣuṇā kaṭhinaṃ gṛhītvā na prasrāvakuṭiḥ va varcuskuṭiḥ va dhūpāgāraṃ praveṣṭavyam |",
    "747:139": "nābhyavakāśe sthātavyam |",
    "747:140": "na bahiḥsīmāṃ gantavyam |",
    "747:141": "sa ced gacchati na tasyāṃ vastavyam |",
    "747:142": "kaṭhināstārako bhikṣuryathāprajñaptānāsamudācārikān dharmān na samādāya vartate |",
    "747:143": "sātisāro bhavati |",
    "747:144": "tataḥ kaṭhināstārakeṇa bhikṣuṇā phālgunamāse paṃcadaśyām punarāroayitavyam |",
    "747:145": "śva āyuṣmantaḥ kaṭhinamuddhariṣyāmi |",
    "747:146": "yūyaṃ svakasvakāni cīvarāṇyadhitiṣṭhateti |",
    "747:147": "yaśca tatra lābhaḥ saṃpannaḥ sa saṃghena bhājayitavyaḥ |",
    "747:148": "āyuṣmānudālī buddhaṃ bhagavantaṃ pṛcchati |",
    "747:149": "katīnāṃ bhadanta kaṭhinamanāstṛtam |",
    "747:150": "paṃcānāmudālin |",
    "747:151": "avārṣikasya varṣācchinnakasya paścimakāvarṣopagatasyānyatra varṣopagatasya tasmin kaṭhine āstīryamāṇe asaṃmukhībhūtasya |",
    "747:152": "apareṣāmapi paṃcānāmanāstṛtam |",
    "747:153": "pārivāsikasya paryuṣitaparivāsasya mānāpyacārikasya caritamānāpyasya śikṣādattakasya ca |",
    "747:154": "katīnāṃ bhadanta naiva lābho nānuśaṃsā |",
    "747:155": "paṃcānāmudālin |",
    "747:156": "adaśanāyotkṣoptakasyāpratikarmaṇāyutkṣiptakasyāpratinisṛṣṭe pāpake dṛṣṭigare utkṣiptakasyānyatra varṣoṣitasya bhinne ca saṃghe adharmapākṣikasya |",
    "747:157": "saṃbahulā bhikṣo janapadacārikāṃ carantaścīrairmuṣitāste'nupūrveṇa śrāvastīmanuprāptāḥ |",
    "747:158": "bhikṣubhirdṛṣṭāḥ |",
    "747:159": "svāgataṃ svāgatamāyuṣmantaḥ |",
    "747:160": "kaccitsukhacaryā |",
    "747:161": "kīdṛśyāyuṣmantaḥ |",
    "747:162": "sukhacaryā |",
    "747:163": "corairmuṣitāḥ smaḥ |",
    "747:164": "asmākamāyuṣmantaḥ prabhūto lābhaḥ saṃpannaḥ |",
    "747:165": "yadi kaṭhinamuddhriyate cīvarairyuṣmāaṃ saṃvibhāgaṃ kurma iti |",
    "747:166": "etatprakaraṇaṃ bhikṣavo bhagavata ārocayanti |",
    "747:167": "bhagavānāha |",
    "747:168": "tasmādanujānāmi corairmuṣitakānāṃ bhuikṣuṇāmarthāya kaṭhinamuddhartavyam |",
    "747:169": "evaṃ ca punaruddhartavyam |",
    "747:170": "śayanāsanaprajñaptiṃ kṛtvā gaṇḍīmākoṭya pṛṣṭavācikayā bhikṣūn samanuyujya sarvasaṃghe saṃniṣaṇṇe asṃnipatite ekena bhikṣuṇā jñaptiṃ kṛtvā karma kartavyam |",
    "747:171": "śṛṇotu bhadantaḥ saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:172": "yāvadevāsminnāvāse samagreṇa saṃghena kaṭhinamāstṛtam |",
    "747:173": "saṃbahulāśca bhikṣavaḥ cīvairmuṣitā āgatāḥ |",
    "747:174": "sa cetsaṃghasya prāpta kālaṃ kṣametānujānīyāt saṃgho yatsaṃghaścorairmuṣitakānāṃ bhikṣūṇāmarthāya kaṭhinamuddharedityeṣā jñaptiḥ |",
    "747:175": "evaṃ ca karma kartavyam |",
    "747:176": "śṛṇotu bhadanta saṃghaḥ |",
    "747:177": "yāvadevāsminnāvāse samagreṇa saṃghena kaṭhinamāstṛtaṃ saṃbahulāśca bhikṣavaścorairmuṣitakā āgatāstatsaṃghaścorairmuṣitakānāṃ bhikṣūṇāmarthāya kaṭhinamuddharati |",
    "747:178": "eṣāmāyuṣmatāṃ kṣamante cīvamuṣitakānāṃ bhikṣūṇāmarthāya kaṭhinamuddharitum te tūṣṇīm |",
    "747:179": "na kṣamante |",
    "747:180": "bhāṣantām |",
    "747:181": "uddhṛtaṃ saṃghena coramuṣitakānāṃ bhikṣūṇāmarthāya |",
    "747:182": "kaṭhinaṃ kṣāntamanujñātaṃ saṃghena yasmāttūṣṇīmevametaddhārayāmi |",
    "747:183": "yasmād yo lābhaḥ saṃpannaḥ sa bhājayitavyaḥ |",
    "747:184": "bhājite yasyā(bhi)",
    "747:185": "pretaṃ tena svakāt pratyaṃśāt coramuṣitakānāṃ bhikṣuṇāṃ saṃvibhāgaḥ kartavyaḥ |",
    "747:186": "uddānam |",
    "747:187": "vitaritam vilikhitaṃ bandhanī gaṇḍūṣaṃ paṭṭikā |",
    "747:188": "upadhiḥ pariṣaṇḍaśca purāṇaṃ saṃnihitaṃ phupphusam ||2||",
    "747:189": "āyuṣmānudālī buddhaṃ bhagavantaṃ pṛccati |",
    "747:190": "labhyaṃ bhadanta vitaritena cīvarakena kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:191": "na labhamudālin |",
    "747:192": "labhyaṃ bhadanta vilikhitena dakaśāṭikācīvareṇa gaṇḍūṣacīvareṇa paṭṭikācīvareṇa plotikācīvareṇa pariṣaṇḍacīvareṇa purāṇacīvareṇa saṃnihitacīvareṇa phupphusacīvareṇa kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:193": "n alabhyamudālin |",
    "747:194": "uddānam |",
    "747:195": "marditaṃ cāpyakālena pudgalasya tricīvaram",
    "747:196": "akalpikamasaṃchinnaṃ na kuryādūnapaṃcakam |",
    "747:197": "asaṃmatamanāstṛtaṃ bahiḥsīme na rohati ||3||",
    "747:198": "āyuṣmānudālī buddhaṃ bhagavantaṃ pṛcchati |",
    "747:199": "labhyaṃ bhadanta marditena cīvareṇa kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:200": "na labhyamudālin |",
    "747:201": "labhyaṃ bhadanta akālacīvareṇa paudgalikayā saṃghāṭyā uttarāsaṃgenāntarvāsenākalpikena ūnapaṃcakena asaṃmatena kaṭhināstārakeṇa bahiḥsīmāsaṃmatena kaṭhinacīvareṇa bahiḥsīmāsaṃmatena kaṭhināstārakeṇ akaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:202": "n alabhyamudālin |",
    "747:203": "uddānam |",
    "747:204": "kālikaṃ cāpi traimāsyamahataṃ caiva kalpitam |",
    "747:205": "ātyayikaṃ pailotikaṃ pudgalasya tricīvaram ||4||",
    "747:206": "labhyaṃ bhadantakālikena cīvareṇa saṃghasya kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:207": "labhyamudālin yo bhadanta traimāsyātyayātsaṃghasya cīvaralābhaḥ saṃpadyate (tena)",
    "747:208": "kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:209": "labhyamudālin |",
    "747:210": "ahatacīvareṇa labhyam |",
    "747:211": "ahatakalpitena labhyam |",
    "747:212": "ātyayikacīvareṇa labhyam |",
    "747:213": "pailotikacīvareṇa labhyam |",
    "747:214": "paulotikayā saṃghāṭyā na labhyam |",
    "747:215": "(labhyaṃ bhadanta paudgalikayā saṃghāṭyā kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:216": "labhyaṃ) sa cetsaṃghena nisṛṣṭo bhavati |",
    "747:217": "evamuttarāsaṃgenāntarvāsena |",
    "747:218": "uddānam |",
    "747:219": "paudgalikaṃ gārhapatikaṃ paṃcakaṃ sādhikapaṃcakam |",
    "747:220": "saṃmatamāstṛtaṃ caiva antaḥsīme varohati ||5||",
    "747:221": "labhyaṃ bhadanta paudgalikena cīvareṇa kaṭhinamāstartum |",
    "747:222": "na labhyamudālin |",
    "747:223": "labhyaṃ sa cetsaṃghe (na)",
    "747:224": "nisṛṣṭo bhavati |",
    "747:225": "gṛhapati cīvareṇa na labhyam |",
    "747:226": "labhyaṃ sa cetsaṃghena nisṛṣṭo bhavati |",
    "747:227": "saṃcakena labhyam |",
    "747:228": "sādhikena paṃcakena labhyam |",
    "747:229": "saṃmatena kaṭhinacīvareṇa kaṭhināstārakeṇa labhyam |",
    "747:230": "antah sīmā saṃmatena kaṭhinacīvareṇa labhyam |",
    "747:231": "antaḥsīmā saṃmatena kaṭhināstārakeṇa labhyam |",
    "747:232": "aṣṭau mātṛkāpadāni kaṭhinoddhārāya saṃvartante |",
    "747:233": "katame aṣṭau |",
    "747:234": "prakramaṇaṃ niṣṭhāpanaṃ saṃniṣṭhāpanaṃ nāśitaṃ śravaṇaṃ sīmātikrāntamāśācchedakaṃ kaṭhinoddhāramevāṣṭamam |",
    "747:235": "prakramaṇāntikaḥ kaṭhinodhāro niṣṭhāpanāntikaḥ saṃniṣṭhāpanāntiko nāśitāntikaḥ śravaṇāntikaḥ sīmātikrāntikaḥ āśācchedakah kaṭhinoddhāra evāṣṭamaḥ |",
    "747:236": "prakramaṇāntikaḥ kaṭhinodvāraḥ katamah |",
    "747:237": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaraḥ samādāya pātracīvaraṃ bahiḥsīmāṃ prakrāmatyapunarāgamanāya |",
    "747:238": "tasya prakramaṇāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||1||",
    "747:239": "niṣṭhāpanā (ntikaḥ)",
    "747:240": "kaṭhinoddhāraḥ katamah |",
    "747:241": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥsīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:242": "ptayeṣyāmi cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:243": "tasyaivaṃ bhavati |",
    "747:244": "na haiva pratyeṣyāmi |",
    "747:245": "apitu cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:246": "tasya niṣṭhāpanāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||2||",
    "747:247": "saṃniṣṭhāpanāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:248": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥsīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:249": "pratyeṣyāmi cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:250": "tasyaivaṃ bhavati |",
    "747:251": "na haiva pratyeṣyāmi nāpī cīvaram kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:252": "tasya saṃniṣṭhāpanāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||3||",
    "747:253": "nāśitāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:254": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥ sīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:255": "pratyeṣyāmi cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:256": "sa tadārabhate |",
    "747:257": "ārabdhaṃ tu naśyati |",
    "747:258": "tasya nāśitāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||4||",
    "747:259": "śravaṇāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:260": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥ sīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:261": "pratyeṣyāṃi cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:262": "samagreṇa ca saṃghena kaṭhinamuddhṛtamiti śrutvā cābhyanumodate |",
    "747:263": "sādhūddhṛtaṃ suṣṭhūddhṛtamiti |",
    "747:264": "tasya śravaṇāntikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||5||",
    "747:265": "sīmāntikrāṇtikaḥ kaṭhinoddhāraḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:266": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥ sīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:267": "pratyeṣyāmi na pratyeṣyāmīti sīmāṃ cātikrāmati |",
    "747:268": "tasya sāīmātikrānti kaṭhinoddhāraḥ ||6||",
    "747:269": "āśācchedakaḥ kaṭhinodhāraḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:270": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛtacīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥ sīmāṃ prakrāmati |",
    "747:271": "pratyeṣyāmi cīvaraṃ kariṣyāmīti |",
    "747:272": "tasya yā sā cīvarapratyāśā sā sarveṇa sarvaṃ samucchidyate |",
    "747:273": "tasyāśācchedakaḥ(kaṭhinpddhāraḥ) ||7||",
    "747:274": "kaṭhinoddhāra evāṣṭamaḥ katamaḥ |",
    "747:275": "yathāpi tadbhikṣurāstīrṇakaṭhinādāvāsādakṛta cīvaro'niṣṭhitacīvaro bahiḥ sīmāṃ prakrāmati cāgatya kaṭhinoddhāraṃ pratyanubhavati |",
    "747:276": "tasya kaṭhinoddhāra evāṣṭamaḥ ||8||",
    "747:277": "uddānam |",
    "747:278": "akṛtena hi viṃśatiṃ vi (pra)",
